Introduction

Public summary: 

By comparing sizes and distances we can scale our solar system all the
way up from the Earth and the Moon, up to our nearest star, and you
might be surprised how far that actually is!

Public visibility: 

Demonstrators

By comparing sizes and distances we can scale our solar system all the
way up from the Earth and the Moon, up to our nearest star, and you
might be surprised how far that actually is!

Useful information

Kit List: 

Golf ball - Moon +
Globe - Earth +
Marbles - Earth/Sun on different scales +
Red foam ball - Jupiter +
Card with pin-prick hole - Sun/Solar system on bigger scales

Packing Away: 

Don't lose your marbles!

